24:39.812 --> 24:41.480 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
Hari Sreenivasan has that.

24:41.513 --> 24:45.784 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: There were new
and more
serious fractures today on the
Intelligence

24:45.818 --> 24:47.519 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
Committee.

24:47.553 --> 24:51.123 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
It's investigating Russian
meddling in last
year's election, and alleged
ties between

24:51.156 --> 24:53.292 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
the Trump campaign and Moscow.

24:53.325 --> 24:57.229 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Now the very direction of the
probe itself
seems in question.

24:57.262 --> 25:00.766 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Here for some more on this is
one of the committee's
Democratic members,
Representative Eric Swalwell

25:00.799 --> 25:02.568 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
of California.

25:02.601 --> 25:06.405 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Congressman, you have said
before that you
feel that Chairman Devin Nunes
has a conflict

25:06.438 --> 25:07.573 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
of interests.

25:07.606 --> 25:08.440 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Do you think he's taking orders
from the White
House?

25:08.474 --> 25:10.142 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
REP.

25:10.175 --> 25:13.212 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
ERIC SWALWELL (D), California: I
think he
betrayed the duty to conduct an
independent,

25:13.245 --> 25:15.013 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
collaborative investigation.

25:15.047 --> 25:18.851 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
We were attacked by Russia this
past election,
and our constituents are
counting on us to

25:18.884 --> 25:20.819 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
get to the bottom of what
happened.

25:20.853 --> 25:26.558 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
He's going off on his own, and
receiving classified
information, not sharing it with
members of

25:26.592 --> 25:30.329 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
the committee, taking it to the
White House,
where the president's campaign
is currently

25:30.362 --> 25:33.198 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
under criminal and
counterintelligence
investigations.

25:33.232 --> 25:37.569 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
I think what we need to do is,
he needs to
find an on-ramp, because this
investigation

25:37.603 --> 25:39.538 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
must continue to go forward.

25:39.571 --> 25:41.407 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
And he must work with Democrats.

25:41.440 --> 25:45.344 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Otherwise, our constituents are
going to ask,
how can you conduct a credible
investigation

25:45.377 --> 25:49.248 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
into the largest attack that our
elections
have ever seen?

25:49.281 --> 25:53.018 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
HARI SREENIVASAN: The
information at the center
of this particular controversy,
he said that

25:53.051 --> 25:57.723 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
he has information of apparent
unmasking of
identified of U.S. persons tied
to the Trump

25:57.756 --> 26:00.292 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
campaign collected under legal
surveillance.

26:00.325 --> 26:03.662 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Have you now seen in the last
couple of days
seen any of this information?

26:03.695 --> 26:05.597 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
